HEADWORD: Susceptor
<hw>Sus*cep"tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. See
<er>Susceptible</er>.]</ety> <def>One who undertakes anything;
specifically, a godfather; a sponsor; a guardian.</def> <rj><au>Puller.
Shipley.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

